Cell["\<\
What about the inverse of this plot?
This is the function tp[ t ], which is sensor time.\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.968230215985426*^9, 3.9682302328161697`*^9}, 
   3.9682303080804453`*^9, {3.968230662276119*^9, 3.968230666423564*^9}, {
